title: [Armundia's Magic Shoppe]
[Armundia's Outfitting]
description: A tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the golden plaster walls, and a deep red stucco ceiling rises overhead.  A knotted woolen rug sits in one corner of an unfinished wooden floor.  There is a heavy wooden desk on one side of the shop and a plain wooden table on the other.
